text: Uyea (pronounced "oe-yë") may refer to: * Uyea, Unst, an uninhabited island south of Unst in Shetland, Scotland * Uyea, Northmavine, an uninhabited island northwest of Mainland, Shetland ==See also== * Uyeasound, a village on Unst overlooking the first Uyea * Uynarey, one of the Shetland islands
title: Uyea
